post_text: It's a 624 Fact - The WBLAHS M3 Math Challenge team, made up of students Sydney Beck, Matthew Chouinard, Kailey Halama, Abbie Nistler, and Cristina Ryberg, was selected as one of the best 145 papers submitted nationwide. (Photo taken on a pre-social-distancing lunch break.) Go Bears!
